A coaching program for photographers

I love coaching photographers worldwide and other 'momtogs' (moms with cameras) like me, so they can reach their goals and dreams, by learning them to work smarter and handing them practical tools they can use in their everyday business.
I love coaching photographers worldwide and other 'momtogs' (moms with cameras) like me, so they can reach their goals and dreams, by learning them to work smarter and handing them practical tools they can use in their everyday business.

1-ON-1 COACHING

Some of the things I’ve helped previous clients with include

Repair & reorganize Lightroom Library

Master the Library module and you’ll be well on your way to becoming an expert on the entire program.

Design & implement a custom backup strategy

There are many ways of backing up photos, you need to find the method that works best for you.

Workflow strategy - from capture to output

A comprehensive look at the essential steps and principles in an effective photo editing workflow with highlights of key tools.

Integration photo-editing software

You're a casual smartphone shooter or a professional using an SLR, software can get the most out of your images.
